## Installation

### Using uv (Recommended)

```bash
# Install as a tool
uv tool install code-recap

# Or run directly without installing
uvx code-recap summarize 2025
```

### Using pip

```bash
pip install code-recap
```

### Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/nrb-tech/code-recap.git
cd code-recap
uv sync --dev

# Run linting
uv run ruff check .
uv run ruff format .
```

### Requirements

- **Python 3.9+**
- **Git** (command line)

